# All case data is stored in Git LFS.
# Extensions are lowercase by repository convention (see README.md).
# If a file with an uppercase extension is ever added, rename it to
# lowercase rather than adding an uppercase pattern here.
*.pwb filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
*.pwd filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
